\begin_inset Formula $\hbar/2$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\mathbf{n}}$
\end_inset

 is a unit vector lying in the 
\begin_inset Formula $xz$
\end_inset

-plane that makes an angle 
\begin_inset Formula $γ$
\end_inset

 with the positive 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

-axis.
 
