\left\langle S_{x}^{2}\right\rangle _{\mathbf{\mathbf{S}\cdot\hat{n}}}=\frac{\hbar^{2}}{4}\left(\cos\left(\frac{\gamma}{2}\right)\langle+|+\sin\left(\frac{\gamma}{2}\right)\langle-|\right)\left(\cos\left(\frac{\gamma}{2}\right)\left|+\right\rangle +\sin\left(\frac{\gamma}{2}\right)\left|-\right\rangle \right)\text{,}
